      <title>中国财政部响应习近平关于在央行开展债券交易的号召</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-finance-ministry-echoes-xi-s-call-for-bond-trading-at-pboc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国财政部表示支持允许央行进行国债交易，重申了习近平主席的一句话，引发了市场对货币策略改变的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-finance-ministry-echoes-xi-s-call-for-bond-trading-at-pboc</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:48:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国地方政府融资工具借贷成本降至历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-23/china-s-lgfv-borrowing-costs-drop-to-record-low-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国账外地方政府债务市场已经出现可能出现转变的迹象。就在几个月前，该行业还被标记为亚洲最大的金融风险，但现在借贷成本已降至历史最低水平。周伟报道“彭博社：中国秀”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-23/china-s-lgfv-borrowing-costs-drop-to-record-low-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金价在经历近两年来最大单日跌幅后再次下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/gold-xauusd-falls-again-after-biggest-daily-slump-in-almost-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中东紧张局势缓和，且有迹象表明美联储将维持较高利率以长期抑制需求，金价在创下近两年来最大单日跌幅后扩大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/gold-xauusd-falls-again-after-biggest-daily-slump-in-almost-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:06:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
