      <title>瑞银罕见地将中国股票评级上调至“增持”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/ubs-upgrades-china-stocks-to-overweight-cuts-taiwan-and-korea-lvboqewq</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团今年罕见地上调了对中国主要股指的增持建议，凸显了市场最终好转的初步乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/ubs-upgrades-china-stocks-to-overweight-cuts-taiwan-and-korea-lvboqewq</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 01:06:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商考虑中东风险缓解，油价小幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周针锋相对的攻击后，有迹象表明以色列和伊朗之间的敌对行动有所缓和，交易员权衡以色列和伊朗之间的下一步行动，油价小幅下跌后几乎没有变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 23:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>珍珠奶茶制造商茶百岛在香港 2024 年最大的首次亮相中暴跌 37%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/bubble-tea-maker-chabaidao-debuts-after-hk-s-biggest-ipo-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国珍珠奶茶制造商四川白茶百岛实业有限公司（又名茶百岛）在香港上市首日股价暴跌超过37%，分析师称竞争加剧和消费者信心依然疲弱是其开局不佳的原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/bubble-tea-maker-chabaidao-debuts-after-hk-s-biggest-ipo-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
